title: 2011 Dutchmen Sport M-275BH 26' Travel Trailer
item_description:
Trailer Details

  • Model: 275BH
  • VIN: 47CTDEN23BT207104

    • Expiration Date: 2/28/2025

  • Trailer Type: Travel Trailer
  • Max Sleep Count: 9

Dimensions

  • Overall Length: 356”
  • Overall Width: 102”
  • Overall Height: 108”

Axles, Brakes, and Tires

  • Suspension: Leaf Spring

  • Brake Type: Electric
  • Number of Wheels: 4
  • Tire Size: ST205/75R14
  • Electric Plug Type: 7-Way Round
  • Hitch: 2 5/16" Ball

Features

  • Side Door Access
  • Patio Awning
  • Queen Bed
  • Sofa Bed
  • Hinged Bunk with Double Bed
  • Dinette
  • Oven/Stove
  • Refrigerator and Freezer 
  • Bathroom with toliet, sink and shower/tub

Note: Certificate of Title, and Transfer Form will be provided at pickup (no Tuesdays). The Bidder shall not bid on behalf of another individual; the Bidder/Purchaser/DMV Registrant must be the same. The Buyer is fully responsible for all aspects of registration, transfer, taxes, and fees due to the DMV.
